  "body": "\r\n- From https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/3116\r\n\r\nexport * is too vague, exposes too many items to consumers. The public API should be though of with care and only expose what we expect to be used.\r\n\r\nOtherwise it's very hard to mantain semver and ensure no breaking changes if all the internals are exposed like YOLO\r\n",
